<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
	<title>中奖</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no" />
	<link rel="icon" href="" type="image/x-icon"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/reset.css" type="text/css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/dgf_style.css" type="text/css"/>
    <script charset="utf-8" src="../js/zepto.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="cover">
		<div class="tips">
			<p>领取成功！</p>
			<div class="get-btn jump-btn">确认</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="dgf-details">
		<div class="text-title">
			<div class="prizes">
				<div>
					<b>7天</b>
					<i>免费会员体验</i>
				</div>
				<div class="prize">
					<img src="" alt="">
				</div>
			</div>
			<em></em>
			<strong>活动规则</strong>
		</div>
		<div class="text-con">
			<form action="" method="post">
				<div class="qq-num">
					<input type="text" placeholder="请输入您想充值会员的QQ号">
				</div>
				<div class="get-btn tip-btn">确认领取</div>	
			</form>
			<ul>
				<li>登录企电视TV客户端云试听·企鹅，</li>
				<li>并在此留下您登录所使用的QQ号</li>
				<li>就能在电视上大屏幕畅享海量院线大片啦</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="text-title">
			<strong>下载指南</strong>
		</div>
		<ol class="download">
			<li>
				<p>登陆http://tv.qq.com下载云试听·企鹅APP，并将其拷贝到U盘中</p>
				<div class="step-pic-li1 clearfix">
					<div class="logo-load">
						<img src="../images/logo_load.png" alt="">
					</div>
					<div class="upan">
						<img src="../images/Upan.png" alt="">
					</div>
				</div>
			</li>
			<li>
				<p>将U盘插入电视或盒子的USB口，进行安装；</p>
				<div class="step-pic-li2 clearfix">
					<div class="upan">
						<img src="../images/Upan.png" alt="">
					</div>
					<div class="list-pic">
						<img src="../images/usb.png" alt="">
					</div>
					<div class="list-pic">
						<img src="../images/television.png" alt="">
					</div>
				</div>
			</li>
			<li>
				<p>在智能电视的应用市场（如：沙发管家、当贝市场、奇珀市场、爱家市场）搜索下载并安装“云视听·企鹅”</p>
				<div class="step-pic-li3 clearfix">
					<div>
						<img src="../images/two_d_code.png" alt="">
					</div>
					<p>听说长按指纹并关注的用户会发光</p>
				</div>
			</li>
		</ol>
	</div>
	<script charset="utf-8" src="../js/common.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
	<script charset="utf-8" src="../src/fx.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
	<script charset="utf-8" src="../src/touch.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
	<script charset="utf-8" src="../js/select.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</body>
</html>